(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Uniform Requirements: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;{!Get_Job_Role.IP_Personal_Protective_Equipment__c}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Job Description:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;{!Get_Job_Role.IP_Job_Description__c}&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Forecasted first weekly pay date:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;{!Get_FORECASTED_PAY_DATE}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Initial hours of work:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;{!Shift_Table}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;The table below outlines pay rate(s) that are applicable to this assignment. Note that pay rates may vary depending on time and date of the shift and other factors. Should the pay rate applicable to your shifts change, we will confirm accordingly.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;{!Compass_Pay_Cycle_Text}&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;{!Rate_Table}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Additional information can also be obtained from your Key Information Document and Flexible Employee Handbook. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;If you have any queries regarding your assignment please feel free to contact me.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Yours sincerely&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;{!Get_S_P